319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:24:55.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n<br />\n唔好留力啊 留咗22年了<br />\n但係聽日要見到大家<br />\n唔好又陷入去前線走會無人頂住 後方走會推前線去死嘅矛盾"},{"pid":"fa8e7ec632617ed240952bcb8ec2562a6f4fcb7f","tid":1370734,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ox6qryh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fox6qryh.jpg&h=060aa51c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bdd6c591a73b6d94e5d06b396371a62d08ccfaf","tid":1370734,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:46:19.000Z","msg":"【1941】元朗西鐵站，近入閘範圍有市民擺放衣物予示威者更換。月台上，乘客候車時齊呼「光復香港，時代革命」、「聽日上環見」。"},{"pid":"ced33de5b1c4876fec9effc2c43101c681664a40","tid":1370734,"uid":96380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a94120f72f9cf4062d63b661e9d0bd984bdf3257","tid":1370734,"uid":81628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:51:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91257129639bd7ed73ac2acf8acb1e9ca17c7767","tid":1370734,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:53:58.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無嘢講 我有權唔解鎖 我要搵律師 我唔簽任何文件 我唔信任何警察 我要警誡記錄 我要食飯 飲水 毛氈 去廁所 我唔舒服要去醫院 我要睇你委任證同編號投訴你</code></pre>"},{"pid":"df8f0be570f0ef8d152fcc8868b32924c824e80d","tid":1370734,"uid":257319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Hzjv8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Hzjv8c.jpg&h=295b0015&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kbcdAzT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkbcdAzT.jpg&h=82aceca2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"773a609a2c53cd2b9ba16bdd665866ec6688a58d","tid":1370734,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOBFfAd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOBFfAd.jpg&h=e67565c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6504915113d3536bb353d764c54fad468de34461","tid":1370734,"uid":245347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:06:38.000Z","msg":"遮打見<br />\n收工到"},{"pid":"b67743292ae8c09a478cec129e115af4450f06bf","tid":1370734,"uid":257319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6504915113d3536bb353d764c54fad468de34461","tid":1370734,"uid":245347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:06:38.000Z","msg":"遮打見<br />\n收工到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:07:48.000Z","msg":"遮打見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2489c74c8db34c97c32c8248fecfec73ace35a","tid":1370734,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:39:03.000Z","msg":"上訴委員會正在進行中 #728遮打花園集會 #齊上齊落 #不撤不散<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNb6bnx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNb6bnx.jpg&h=707026bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vda3dAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVda3dAV.jpg&h=c4eec04e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YrkyAPi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYrkyAPi.jpg&h=166a7bc2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ae31564c8ec315ee600e6b38d80651693d988ed","tid":1370734,"uid":257319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T12:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vvN8892.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvvN8892.jpg&h=28a7c180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方反對的理由非同小可，嚴重侵蝕港人的憲制權利，必須推翻警方的決定，捍衛《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\n按照警方的反對通知書條文，警方反對遊行及終點集會的理由只有一個，就是以往類似議題的遊行集會，在結束後都發生衝突。<br />\n<br />\n警方這個理由，等同封殺以後所有與反送中有關的公眾活動，是明目張膽地打壓異見，剝奪《基本法》賦予香港不同政見市民平等享受的集會自由。<br />\n<br />\n7.28 遮打花園集會主辦方呼籲所有捍衛港人基本權利的市民，出席獲警方允許舉行的合法活動，在下午三時到遮打花園集會，「港人必須企出來，用雙腳捍衛自己的遊行集會權利。」"},{"pid":"bc6e97ed97f2041a0be3aee8a5706294fbc201e1","tid":1370734,"uid":115264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64be02069761eca914951590b31b12465e9c60a6","tid":1370734,"uid":115264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f679b5280e41edab7e17d13f339c8d39a4b4333","tid":1370734,"uid":65611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:07:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7e903eff6b51fb585e9b933140bacd837102bea4","tid":1370734,"uid":65611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:11:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"beef1a9d2fcda8c27900299417a8e597c0f5bb7f","tid":1370734,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cF53d3s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcF53d3s.jpg&h=6807f23b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0c1dab48aa4238902866f379ae0d2186ee3994fe","tid":1370734,"uid":115264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:10:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5804df2ecd08bd034695439af335bac81c084b63","tid":1370734,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sTMRn0L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsTMRn0L.jpg&h=1bb08ee9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"585b47eb9b8fcfef1addeca2697709e5873da222","tid":1370734,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"依家次次都話遊完行就有事發生<br />\n就ban<br />\n應該以後都係咁"},{"pid":"3de632587af0b1f9ee183946ef3a824184a59939","tid":1370734,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:36:11.000Z","msg":"我知大家應該可能仲喺元朗或者啱啱出緊嚟嘅路上<br />\n我哋依家努力做緊啲文宣<br />\n希望可以話俾人知今日究竟完我發生咗啲咩事<br />\n<br />\n同時間上訴委員會已經啱啱開完<br />\n我哋申請遊行嘅上訴已經被駁回<br />\n<br />\n以下係我哋嘅發言重點：<br />\n<br />\n剛才都多次強調<br />\n發出反對通知書前<br />\n警方無要求過更改任何內容<br />\n<br />\n我哋及在場某一兩位委員<br />\n都有提出好多有建設性的修改<br />\n都一樣被駁回<br />\n<br />\n警方指，逢星期六日<br />\n只需超過 2000 人的遊行<br />\n就會係高危活動<br />\n<br />\n警方根本發出緊訊息俾市民<br />\n索性不要不反對通知<br />\n不斷去增加表達意見的權利的門檻<br />\n<br />\n明天好可能<br />\n是最後一次以反送中的議題可進行的和平集會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開完會後我哋嘅心情<br />\n<br />\n1. 有咩心情？<br />\n擔憂人權自由情況<br />\n一早預咗呢個結果<br />\n因委員會成員由建制派組成<br />\n如明天有市民用雙腳捍衛其遊行權利<br />\n劉生絕對支持<br />\n<br />\n2. 擔唔擔心反對通知書變成常態？<br />\n警方講明週末超過 2000 人的遊行就係高風險<br />\n所以唔係擔心，而係高機會<br />\n希望大家唔好驚<br />\n我哋要保持意志去捍衛遊行自由<br />\n無人可以剝奪<br />\n<br />\n3. 我哋仲想唔想遊行？<br />\n我有意向去進行遊行，亦會義無反顧企喺市民嗰邊，但見到元朗，<br />\n原來警察會對行街的市民，會採用咁過份武力的時候，我在考慮，我呼籲大家遊行的話，就會增加危險，。<br />\n<br />\n4.成個上訴委員會嘅最重點<br />\n警方最大問題係 週末 超過2000人 遊行<br />\n就係高危活動，而佢地就係用呢個原因駁回上訴。<br />\n<br />\n5 呼籲三點參與遮打集會，追究警方開槍責任"},{"pid":"7bab201c285c6f4601f9444d3c871bf6e030cb2b","tid":1370734,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3de632587af0b1f9ee183946ef3a824184a59939","tid":1370734,"uid":257319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:36:11.000Z","msg":"我知大家應該可能仲喺元朗或者啱啱出緊嚟嘅路上<br />\n我哋依家努力做緊啲文宣<br />\n希望可以話俾人知今日究竟完我發生咗啲咩事<br />\n<br />\n同時間上訴委員會已經啱啱開完<br />\n我哋申請遊行嘅上訴已經被駁回<br />\n<br />\n以下係我哋嘅發言重點：<br />\n<br />\n剛才都多次強調<br />\n發出反對通知書前<br />\n警方無要求過更改任何內容<br />\n<br />\n我哋及在場某一兩位委員<br />\n都有提出好多有建設性的修改<br />\n都一樣被駁回<br />\n<br />\n警方指，逢星期六日<br />\n只需超過 2000 人的遊行<br />\n就會係高危活動<br />\n<br />\n警方根本發出緊訊息俾市民<br />\n索性不要不反對通知<br />\n不斷去增加表達意見的權利的門檻<br />\n<br />\n明天好可能<br />\n是最後一次以反送中的議題可進行的和平集會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開完會後我哋嘅心情<br />\n<br />\n1. 有咩心情？<br />\n擔憂人權自由情況<br />\n一早預咗呢個結果<br />\n因委員會成員由建制派組成<br />\n如明天有市民用雙腳捍衛其遊行權利<br />\n劉生絕對支持<br />\n<br />\n2. 擔唔擔心反對通知書變成常態？<br />\n警方講明週末超過 2000 人的遊行就係高風險<br />\n所以唔係擔心，而係高機會<br />\n希望大家唔好驚<br />\n我哋要保持意志去捍衛遊行自由<br />\n無人可以剝